NonReentrancy
├── GuardedIncrement
│   ├── when called once
│   │   └── it should increment the counter by 1
│   └── when called twice sequentially
│       └── it should increment the counter to 2
├── ReentrancyProtection
│   └── when a guarded function attempts to reenter itself (direct or via external call)
│       └── it should revert with Reentrancy
└── GuardResetOnRevert
    └── when a guarded function reverts after enter and before exit
        └── it should clear the guard so that future guarded calls succeed

